sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as 관리자
    participant UI as React UI (Permissions)
    participant Preload as electronAPI
    participant IPC as IPC Main (setupIpcHandlers)
    participant UC as AppUseCases
    participant Repo as PrismaPenaltyRepository
    participant DB as SQLite DB

    Admin->>UI: 제재 목록에서 대상자의 '제재 해제(Trash)' 아이콘 클릭
    activate UI
    UI-->>Admin: 해제 확인 대화상자 출력
    Admin->>UI: '확인' 버튼 클릭
    UI->>Preload: invoke('penalty:delete', penaltyId)
    activate Preload
    Preload->>IPC: IPC 채널 전송
    activate IPC
    IPC->>UC: penalty.delete(penaltyId)
    activate UC
    UC->>Repo: delete(penaltyId)
    activate Repo
    Repo->>DB: prisma.penalty.delete({ where: { id } })
    activate DB
    DB-->>Repo: 삭제 완료
    deactivate DB
    Repo-->>UC: 완료
    deactivate Repo
    UC-->>IPC: 완료
    deactivate UC
    IPC-->>Preload: { success: true }
    deactivate IPC
    Preload-->>UI: Promise Resolve
    deactivate Preload
    UI->>UI: 제재 목록에서 해당 행 제거
    UI-->>Admin: 제재 해제 완료 — 정상 권한 복구됨
    deactivate UI
